widgets_values: A close-up of a car product advertisement, with a bottle of black anti-fog and waterproof product and box placed on the hood of the car, a neatly folded towel underneath, and a yellow sponge next to it. The shiny surface of the hood in the foreground reflects the surrounding trees and sky, highlighting its high quality. In the background is a modern building, adding a high-end and professional atmosphere. Natural light enhances the smooth texture, creating a realistic and luxurious product advertising feel.

The glass bottle is placed on a large transparent glass plate in the left corner. (There is a clear water flow on the surface, which enhances the fluidity of the liquid), giving a vivid impression. The background is dark brown, and a sharp golden light penetrates from the upper right to the lower left glass, making the color of the bottle and the water droplets more prominent. The overall picture adopts a minimalist style. The use of light increases the three-dimensional sense and impact of the bottle, attracting the audience's attention and significantly highlighting the uniqueness of the bottle and the ceiling.

Some simple flowers are placed next to the glass bottle, and the background is warm and soft, creating a fresh and natural feeling. The beige and yellow tones of the background complement the flowers, giving a relaxed and elegant atmosphere, which may convey the gentle and organic nature of the product.

A skin care product is placed on a stone slab, surrounded by fine sand dunes, with a bent dead tree behind it, and a warm orange-yellow gradient background, creating a sunset desert atmosphere, and a few oranges with leaves, emphasizing the natural plant ingredients of the product. This composition combines earth tones and minimalist style, making the product look high-end and pure, while conveying a warm and comfortable feeling of use.

The glass products are placed in the snow, with a blurred pine background behind them, creating a winter atmosphere. The style is Christmas, fresh and natural, with attention to details, using the texture of the snow scene and the product to highlight the coolness and warmth of the festival.Color: mainly warm amber (drinks) and cold white (snow), forming a cold and warm contrast with the green pine trees in the background;
